      "title": "Golden Armor",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Golden_Armor\">Golden Armor</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Golden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Golden Armor\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Golden_Saint_Armor_Female.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/06/SR-item-Golden_Saint_Armor_Female.jpg/200px-SR-item-Golden_Saint_Armor_Female.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/06/SR-item-Golden_Saint_Armor_Female.jpg/300px-SR-item-Golden_Saint_Armor_Female.jpg 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/0/06/SR-item-Golden_Saint_Armor_Female.jpg/400px-SR-item-Golden_Saint_Armor_Female.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Golden_Saint_Armor_Female.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A female <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Imperial\" title=\"Skyrim:Imperial\">Imperial</a> wearing Golden Saint Armor</div></div></div>\n<p>Golden armor is a variety of heavy armor. The armor is on par with <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Orcish\" title=\"Skyrim:Orcish\">Orcish</a> equipment, except for the cuirass which is better and the shield which is worse.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable striped\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=