ot.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Gold_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Gold Ingot\">Gold</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra Heart.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/b/b1/SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png/24px-SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/b/b1/SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png/36px-SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/b/b1/SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png/48px-SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Daedra_Heart\" title=\"Skyrim:Daedra Heart\">Daedra Heart</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingot-Refined Moonstone.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/87/SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png/24px-SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/87/SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png/36px-SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/8/87/SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png/48px-SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Moonstone_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Moonstone Ingot\">Moonstone</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/24px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/36px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/48px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Leather_Strips\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Leather Strips\">Strips</a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a hr