    "3": {
      "title": "Golden Weapons",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Golden_Weapons\">Golden Weapons</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Golden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Golden Weapons\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Golden_Saint_Weapons.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/78/SR-item-Golden_Saint_Weapons.jpg/200px-SR-item-Golden_Saint_Weapons.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/78/SR-item-Golden_Saint_Weapons.jpg/300px-SR-item-Golden_Saint_Weapons.jpg 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/7/78/SR-item-Golden_Saint_Weapons.jpg/400px-SR-item-Golden_Saint_Weapons.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Golden_Saint_Weapons.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Golden Saint Weapons</div></div></div>\n<p>Golden weapons are slightly inferior to <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Malachite\" title=\"Skyrim:Malachite\">Glass</a> weapons. They do the same damage as <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Elven#Elven_Weapons\" title=\"Skyrim:Elven\">Elven Weapons</a> for higher critical damage and lower weight, apart from the bow which is weaker than a <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dwarven#Dwarven_Bow\" title=\"Skyrim:Dwarven\">Dwarven Bow</a>. \n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">ID\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Damage\"><img alt=\"Damage\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/22px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/33px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/44px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Crit.<br /><a href=\"/wiki/File:SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Damage\"><img alt=\"Damage\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/22px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/33px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/44px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Speed\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Reach\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:thick; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"5\">Raw Materials\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:thick; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"2\">Delta\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Ratio\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th sty